## Summary

| Aspect | Status | Notes |
|--------|--------|-------|
| Overall Architecture | ✅ Correct | Well-structured, layers properly separated |
| Data Flow | ✅ Correct | All components properly wired |
| Multiview Matcher | ✅ Working | Correctly classifies strong/weak matches |
| Binding Manager | ⚠️ Too Strict | Uses different thresholds than matcher |
| Evidence Gate | ✅ Working | Quality filtering is appropriate |
| Source Auth | ✅ Working | UNC status expected for close faces |
| Close-Up Recognition | ⚠️ Slow | Due to threshold mismatch, not wiring issues |

The system is **robust and correctly implemented**. The delay is a configuration/threshold issue, not a logic or wiring error.
